{"tid":753527,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[傑利蠑螈] 2019年區議會重新劃界","createTime":"2018-07-23T16:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:15:37.000Z","uid":54627,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7399158fa5c835f3a5f53e236ae9c6055bf46a","tid":753527,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"下年又到四年一度嘅區議會選舉，選管會今日公佈新選區劃界圖，雖然仆街選管會主席馮驊強調重劃選區「絕對無政治考慮」，不過傻嘅一睇啲變咗嘅界就睇到選管會用緊臭名昭著嘅傑利蠑螈（Gerrymander）去幫保皇黨進一步增加係區議會嘅影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">WIKI：<br />\n傑利蠑螈是一個來自美國的政治術語，指以不公平的選區劃分方法操縱選舉，致使投票結果有利於某方。這個政治術語源自1812年美國馬薩諸塞州州長埃爾布里奇&middot;格里將某一選區劃分成不尋常的蠑螈（salamander）狀，以讓民主共和黨得勝。當時被重劃的選區中，有一選區形狀特別怪異，有如蠑螈（一種長得蜥蜴的兩棲動物），格里的政敵於是將格里（Gerry）姓氏與蠑螈的字尾（mander）組合成「gerrymandering」（傑利蠑螈），用來影射為照顧黨派利益，不公平畫分選區的方式，此後沿用於世。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個政治舉動係觀塘區議會，著名嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">建制大票倉</span></strong></span>裡面睇得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次明顯所有俾人搞嘅都係民主派嘅選區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">J03 啟業</span></strong></span><br />\n2015年概況：<br />\n選區由公屋啟業邨、居屋啟泰苑同私樓得寶花園組成，選民架構大概由中產稍為佔優<br />\n當時由<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯歐陽均諾</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">民主黨林誠</span>爭奪，最終民建聯以200票小勝<br />\n<br />\n2019年：<br />\n加入建制票倉彩盈邨四座樓，令民主派下屆係啟業選區更加難選<br />\n同時，原本係歸入J06 雙彩嘅個四座樓係抽走咗之後，剩低果個彩德邨獨立成區<br />\n彩德邨係新移民邨，基本上民主派無可能贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/235017_2e7ad709cc0cf8162ed276826bc2ea6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F235017_2e7ad709cc0cf8162ed276826bc2ea6e.png&h=34321f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">J10 安利</span></strong></span><br />\n2015年概況：<br />\n選區由公屋順利邨、順安邨組成，區議員係做咗20幾年嘅民主派蔡澤鴻<br />\n當時由<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯梁騰丰</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">民主派蔡澤鴻</span>爭奪，蔡澤鴻最後贏500票到<br />\n<br />\n2019年：<br />\n特登將新移民聚居地安泰邨嘅兩座樓塞落去（此舉已經違反選管會所謂嘅『維持社區完整性』原則），加埋啲蛇齋餅糉，下屆民建聯應該可以反Cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/000003_e5445fce40e6b6597312ac49bf301cd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F000003_e5445fce40e6b6597312ac49bf301cd3.png&h=b32b10f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">J23 翠翔</span></strong></span><br />\n2015年概況：<br />\n區議員係民主派謝淑珍，由2011年連任至今<br />\n當時由<span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會黃啟燊</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">民主派謝淑珍</span>爭奪，工賊會最終只係輸200幾票<br />\n<br />\n2019年：<br />\n將原本<strong>完整</strong>嘅高怡邨分拆，係翠翔選區加入兩座高怡邨嘅公屋，意味著工聯會係借助呢兩座新增選民中反勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/001219_0f185e3146718abf2a67baefbad87062.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F001219_0f185e3146718abf2a67baefbad87062.png&h=a697015e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4dd164db113e76910bd7dd8ad0206148515b264a","tid":753527,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"512c928696063404ee2eacb1b57b489a71fce9cf","tid":753527,"uid":33635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"到底有無得反對？"},{"pid":"5c82bf6fa8a257d24c71c0b583665ac794384cf6","tid":753527,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"啟晴個邊點睇<br />\n我覺得啟德貼住新蒲崗應該劃入九東"},{"pid":"c7cb4e87fad7baf62e2f5e7cf4e2246cdb22f28c","tid":753527,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c82bf6fa8a257d24c71c0b583665ac794384cf6","tid":753527,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"啟晴個邊點睇<br />\n我覺得啟德貼住新蒲崗應該劃入九東"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好關區選事&hellip;<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"0ff9c1049fdc30f6df61810d0d7c97ea39535fd7","tid":753527,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512c928696063404ee2eacb1b57b489a71fce9cf","tid":753527,"uid":33635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"到底有無得反對？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"市民可於8月21日或之前，透過郵寄（灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓選管會秘書處）、傳真（2511 1682）或電郵（eacenq@reo.gov.hk），就建議選區分界及名稱遞交書面意見。選管會並將於8月1日及3日，分別在深水埗及沙田舉行諮詢大會。選管會將考慮在諮詢期間收集到的意見，然後向行政長官提交正式選區分界及名稱建議。<br />\n<br />\n不過99%係無用，睇番上屆諮詢，多數嘅意見佢係會直接Ban咗佢<br />\n（e.g. <a href=\"https://www.eac.gov.hk/ch/distco/2015dc_boundary_v1_report.htm#vol3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2015dc_boundary_v1_report.htm%23vol3&d=EKY3ipczev8%2BQ%2F%2FBW9asO2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=5f6a3e5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.gov.hk/ch/distco/2015dc_boundary_v1_report.htm#vol3</a> 附錄二－書面及口頭申 述摘要，以及選管會的觀點）<br />\n<br />\n而且佢劃界工作係閉門做車，根本外人完全唔知佢係用乜嘢準則，簡單來講即係政府同建制私下打龍通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a104b0d731cc8cf6db16edd63751040fbb79ce9","tid":753527,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"根本好多都做唔到「維持社區完整性」<br />\n安達有兩座分咗去北秀茂坪"},{"pid":"8426c801a0468ab66525b9f1ba3e61d5b8e79803","tid":753527,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a104b0d731cc8cf6db16edd63751040fbb79ce9","tid":753527,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"根本好多都做唔到「維持社區完整性」<br />\n安達有兩座分咗去北秀茂坪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:28:02.000Z","msg":"擺明就搬票倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab03e7d58550e7a7877f2c3dba84b0fd8a5ebf9","tid":753527,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cb4e87fad7baf62e2f5e7cf4e2246cdb22f28c","tid":753527,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c82bf6fa8a257d24c71c0b583665ac794384cf6","tid":753527,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"啟晴個邊點睇<br />\n我覺得啟德貼住新蒲崗應該劃入九東"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好關區選事&hellip;<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"選管會之前提及過佢哋基本上唔會對18區嘅邊界做任何調整，所以而家個嗰分界就係82年第一次區選嗰陣嘅樣，當然啟德仲唔劃入九龍東係完全Outdate嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n香港無法定嘅分區，所謂18區即係區議會嘅分區嚟，所以係關區選事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43857c761004c0cef25f56d5d5c261b418d56eb","tid":753527,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"沙田區仲搞笑啦，將山頂劃兩幢入山下面都做得出，中間仲要隔左一個選區"},{"pid":"deafbba4c1def40fd75f518dde9a44e995926555","tid":753527,"uid":71122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"話說呢，謝淑珍嗰區係踢走咗高翔苑嗰幾幢公務員宿舍，但係加咗隔離區油麗邨兩幢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0128ff14f2e81c05e843183e904bd85b2095a63","tid":753527,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b43857c761004c0cef25f56d5d5c261b418d56eb","tid":753527,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"沙田區仲搞笑啦，將山頂劃兩幢入山下面都做得出，中間仲要隔左一個選區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:51:04.000Z","msg":"鉛水邨？佢咁劃正路喎<br />\n乙明少人，水仔開唔到兩個獨立選區，緊係搞丘文俊<br />\nlm睇鄧家彪成功轉區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid